 -- Esteban M. Navas Martín <algodelinux@gmail.com>  06 Feb 2018 13:51:00 +0100

pkgsync (1.44) unstable; urgency=low

  * Modified nightly-pkgsync to inhibit shutdown or reboot if systemd is installed

